press 'Look behind' (C/R3 by default) to activate
press WASD buttons or Left thumbstick to navigate
Use scroll wheel/Mouse or Right thumbstick to zoom
press E/Q or L1/R1 to modify speed

press 'Fire' (Mouse button 1/Right trigger by default) to Obliterate
